/* Untitled

Hi, I'm Jeremy. I build stuff for the internet.

I'm a Senior Full Stack Javascript developer since 2008. My job is to help companies around the world to build successful products and deliver great user experiences.

I have considerable expertise in Front End development with react, redux, nodejsand react-native and have worked with a number of different frameworks and languages thorough my career.

I've been exclusively working remotely since 2016 and have been a supporter of the remote community since then.

Companies I've worked with: Jour, Waldo.io, Hivy (YC W17, acquired by Managed by Q), eFounders, Viadeo.

If you’d like to chat feel free to email me.

*/ const Index = () => (
